  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl24_LabelType\">You can use your natural poison to augment the spells you cast.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>Vishkanya</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl24_LabelType\">You can spend a use of your toxic racial trait and use a bit of your toxic saliva or blood as an additional material component for a spell with the poison descriptor (see <em>Pathfinder RPG Ultimate Magic</em>) to increase the spell&rsquo;s save DC by 1.</span></p>",
